        <fieldNames>Proposal_Sent_On__c</fieldNames>
        <fieldNames>Rev_Rec_Terms__c</fieldNames>
        <fieldNames>Deal_Registration_Status__c</fieldNames>
        <info>&lt;p&gt;1.Identify and fill in Account Name (sold-to), Ultimate Consignee(UC) and Distributor.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2.Add Products (&amp;quot;Products&amp;quot; in Related Tab)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3.Identify Primary contact (receives Quote) (&amp;quot;Contact Roles&amp;quot; in Related Tab) &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4.If Illumina is selling directly to the UC, select the checkbox labeled Direct Sale to UC &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5.Provide Rev Rec Term to reflect revenue recognition details for this opportunity. Must be completed by PAM/TAM.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;6.Use the &amp;quot;Quote Request&amp;quot; tab when you need a quote proposal (In Activity panel, change the assignee if needed)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;7.Enter all segmentation (see Segmentation Information section)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Account (Sold-To) – 与最终用户买卖的代理商&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;代理商与最终用户之间的交易模式：人民币→此处填境内注册的代理商；美金→此处填境外注册的代理商 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ultimate Consignee (end customer) – 最终用户&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Distributor – 签DA的代理商&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Manual quote&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Provide manual Quote number and reason (Quote section) and fill in &amp;quot;Quote Generated on&amp;quot; date field&lt;/p&gt;</info>
        <picklistValueName>Develop</picklistValueName>
    </pathAssistantSteps>
    <pathAssistantSteps>
        <fieldNames>Purchase_Order_Number__c</fieldNames>
        <fieldNames>Purchase_Order_Received_On__c</fieldNames>
        <info>&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Reminder&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Update Close Date and/or Forecast Category, if needed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Purchase Order Number and Date will be auto-populated once received, and opportunity will close automatically.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Forecast Guidance&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Default Forecast Category for &amp;#39;Finalize&amp;#39; stage is &amp;#39;Commit&amp;#39;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</info>
